=\"128357984\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/resurrection?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Resurrection</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note6b\" data-full-marker=\"6b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357986\" id=\"note6b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Jesus Christ, Judge</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357987\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/redemption?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Redemption</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note7b\" data-full-marker=\"7b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357988\" id=\"note7b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/world?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> World</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note7c\" data-full-marker=\"7c\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357989\" id=\"note7c_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.15?lang=eng#p15\">Mosiah 13:15</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.30?lang=eng#p30\">D&amp;C 58:30</a>. </span><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/justification?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Justification</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note7d\" data-full-marker=\"7d\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357990\" id=\"note7d_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/27.4?lang=eng#p4\">Ps. 27:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.21?lang=eng#p21\">1 Ne. 10:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.50-62?lang=eng#p62\">D&amp;C 76:62 (50–62)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.57?lang=eng#p57\">Moses 6:57</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"e\" id=\"note7e\" data-full-marker=\"7e\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357991\" id=\"note7e_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.28?lang=eng#p28\">Mosiah 2:28</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"f\" id=\"note7f\" data-full-marker=\"7f\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357992\" id=\"note7f_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/deut/6.4?lang=eng#p4\">Deut. 6:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3.20?lang=eng#p20\">Gal. 3:20</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.28?lang=eng#p28\">D&amp;C 20:28</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"g\" id=\"note7g\" data-full-marker=\"7g\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357993\" id=\"note7g_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/happiness?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Happiness</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357994\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/gospel?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Gospel</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note8b\" data-full-marker=\"8b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357995\" id=\"note8b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.4-13?lang=eng#p4\">2 Ne. 29:4 (4–13)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note8c\" data-full-marker=\"8c\">\n<p data-aid=\"128357996\" id=\"note8c_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.20-2